*********************************
*** Istructions for streaming ***
*********************************

0) Please, read the manpage


0.0) Before the compilation

0.0.1) Manpage

[some@prompt nemesi-x.y.z]$ man docs/nemesi.1


0.1) Before the installation

0.1.2) Manpage PostScript (TM) version

[some@prompt nemesi-x.y.z]$ gv docs/nemesi.1.ps.gz

0.1.3) Manpage HTML version

[some@prompt nemesi-x.y.z]$ galeon docs/nemesi.1.html

0.1.3) Manpage pdf version

[some@prompt nemesi-x.y.z]$ ggv docs/nemesi.1.pdf


0.2) After the installation

0.2.1) Manpage

[some@prompt nemesi-x.y.z]$ man nemesi

If something goes wrong, check your man path configuration.

0.1.2) Manpage PostScript (TM) version

[some@prompt nemesi-x.y.z]$ gv <some-prefix>/nemesi/docs/nemesi.1.ps.gz

or (RPM installation)

[some@prompt nemesi-x.y.z]$ gv /usr/share/doc/nemesi-x.y.z/nemesi.1.ps.gz

0.1.3) Manpage HTML version

[some@prompt nemesi-x.y.z]$ galeon <some-prefix>/nemesi/docs/nemesi.1.html

or (RPM installation)

[some@prompt nemesi-x.y.z]$ galeon /usr/share/doc/nemesi-x.y.z/nemesi.1.html

0.1.3) Manpage PDF version

[some@prompt nemesi-x.y.z]$ gv <some-prefix>/nemesi/doc/nemesi.1.pdf

or (RPM installation)

[some@prompt nemesi-x.y.z]$ gv /usr/share/doc/nemesi-x.y.z/nemesi.1.pdf

*********************************
*** Istructions for compiling ***
*********************************

1) Please, I'm in hurry to stream

[some@prompt nemesi-x.y.z]$ ./configure
[some@prompt nemesi-x.y.z]$ make
[some@prompt nemesi-x.y.z]$ su
[same@prompt nemesi-x.y.z]# make install

2) Available options for configure:

2.1) Warnings levels

2.1.1) --enable-warnings
2.1.2) --enable-warnings=normal (2.1.1 equivalent)
2.1.3) --enable-warnings=pedantic
2.1.4) --enable-warnings=none [default]

2.2) Error levels

2.2.1) --enable-errors
2.2.2) --enable-errors=normal (2.2.1 equivalent)
2.2.3) --enable-errors=pedantic
2.2.4) --enable-errors=none [default]

2.3) Optimization levels

2.3.1) --enable-optimize [default]
2.3.2) --enable-optimize=normal (2.3.1 equivalent)
2.3.3) --enable-optimize=poor
2.3.4) --enable-optimize=full
2.3.5) --enable-optimize=super
2.3.6) --enable-optimize=none

2.4) Debug

2.4.1) --enable-debug
2.4.2) --enable-debug=yes (2.4.1 equivalent)
2.4.3) --enable-debug=no [default]

2.5) GCC3

2.5.1) --enable-gcc3
2.5.2) --enable-gcc3=yes (2.5.1 equivalent)
2.5.3) --enable-gcc3=no [default]

2.6) SDL library [default]

2.6.1) --enable-sdl [default]
2.6.2) --enable-sdl=yes (2.6.1 equivalent)
2.6.3) --enable-sdl=no

3) Contacts

3.1) Meet us on #lscube on irc.freenode.net
3.2) Mailing list omsp-developers@streaming.polito.it

Enjoy!
